{"tha-ap39:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap39:0.2":"Kundadhanavagga ","tha-ap39:0.3":"Lasunadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap39:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap39:1.2":"tapaso asaham tada; ","tha-ap39:1.3":"Lasunam upajivami, ","tha-ap39:1.4":"lasunam mayhabhojanam. ","tha-ap39:2.1":"Khariyo purayitvana, ","tha-ap39:2.2":"sangharamamagacchaham; ","tha-ap39:2.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap39:2.4":"sanghassa lasunam adam. ","tha-ap39:3.1":"Vipassissa naraggassa, ","tha-ap39:3.2":"sasane niratassaham; ","tha-ap39:3.3":"Sanghassa lasunam datva, ","tha-ap39:3.4":"kappam saggamhi modaham. ","tha-ap39:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap39:4.2":"lasunam yamadam tada; ","tha-ap39:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap39:4.4":"lasunassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap39:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap39:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap39:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap39:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma lasunadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap39:7.1":"Lasunadayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}